# Design Context

Read before any UI, marketing, or visual work. Impeccable commands load these automatically.

- **Strategy:** [`PRODUCT.md`](./PRODUCT.md) — register, users, voice, anti-references, principles
- **Visual system:** [`DESIGN.md`](./DESIGN.md) — colors, typography, components, do's/don'ts

**Quick reference**
- Register: **brand** (marketing/pSEO leads; app follows)
- Personality: sharp, technical, confident (Linear/Stripe register)
- Anti-references: AI hype marketing — no neon, robots, "powered by AI", glassmorphism
- Accent: emerald on slate-950 dark canvas; restrained (≤10% of screen)
- Fonts: Geist Sans + Geist Mono — do not override with Arial
- Accessibility: WCAG 2.1 AA

For design iteration: `/impeccable polish`, `/impeccable critique`, `/impeccable live`
